This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and pose estimation. The use of regression forests and template matching also suggests that it could belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of latent variables, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on datasets containing images and videos, which could also place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
